data.meta_description: Scenes include drilling and blasting of Diamond Reef, at the foot of the Battery in the New York City Harbor. Men check drill bit hammer cables, also a view of a cable pully head. The drill is shown being lowered into a guide, while a voice describes the action. Also, explosives are loaded into a hole. Men splice electronic fuse wires together, and an underwater explosion occurs. The city skyline is shown in the back ground. A man pushes the electric dynamite magneto, or plunger. The barge is shown with drilling rigs.
